{"tid":2188293,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳麥佳亞求歸隊遭拒","createTime":"2020-09-04T06:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T10:57:33.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ea11a1892f70f98c4380db9f53a1ffdf16b20aca","tid":2188293,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:43:38.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】英格蘭代表隊領隊修夫基力排眾議，拒絕答應讓哈利麥佳亞出席本月的歐國聯賽事。<br />\n<br />\n英格蘭國腳後衛哈利麥佳亞（Harry Maguire）上月底在希臘因襲警等罪被捕，雖然後來提出上訴並可以回國，但仍然被領隊修夫基剔除出最新的代表隊名單。據悉，哈利麥佳亞和部份教練團成員向修夫基提出讓他出戰本輪歐國聯，但遭到對方拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n英格蘭足總高層也不希望哈利麥佳亞太早歸隊，修夫基選擇聽從上層的建議。據悉，哈利麥佳亞在球季開鑼前，都不可能重返代表隊，希望這位曼聯隊長能夠先冷靜下來，再披上三獅兵團戰衣。<br />\n<br />\n英格蘭代表隊本月有兩場歐國聯賽事，分別是下周日作客冰島和下周三作客丹麥；10月則分別對比利時和丹麥。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"1fb792ae9f73bb00c76d1c74492e7702cfbd591e","tid":2188293,"uid":73340,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:50:35.000Z","msg":"CLS<br />\n咁鐘意返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846fe4e762e22bacafc1253bb90aab3e0ecd4413","tid":2188293,"uid":238214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fb792ae9f73bb00c76d1c74492e7702cfbd591e","tid":2188293,"uid":73340,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:50:35.000Z","msg":"CLS<br />\n咁鐘意返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:52:46.000Z","msg":"太公波. 仲要冇錢的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d905aaf8446ef27aaa9a46b2ff3d277c9de57904","tid":2188293,"uid":115467,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:53:51.000Z","msg":"驚俾人發現無咗佢踢得仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713dc380ecf7e64cd85f451cee2be0bd9d6204f7","tid":2188293,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T07:46:34.000Z","msg":"一陣比冰島3:0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos